# Pen-path square: edges are exactly straight on the *pen's* trace.
# Corners become arcs of radius |pen_body| (the unavoidable fillet for an
# off-axis pen). Targets are world coordinates of the four corners; place
# them well outside the pen-to-axle distance so each leg is reachable.
goto 30 0
goto 30 30
goto 0 30
goto -10 0
